  "notes": "Mt. Mortar 1F Outside (20x18 blocks, 40x36 tiles, confirmed: MountMortar1FOutside.blk = 360 bytes). The exterior face of Mt. Mortar, a large mountain between Ecruteak and Mahogany. Three entrances from Route 42 line the south edge (warps 3/4/5 on Route 42). The outside area has open rocky terrain with a water channel running through it — Surf is required to access the water. Connections: nine warps total — three to Route 42 (south exits), four into 1F Inside, one up to 2F Inside, one down to B1F. Items: Ether, Revive (both visible pokeball sprites), one hidden Hyper Potion. Tileset: TILESET_DARK_CAVE. Music: MUSIC_UNION_CAVE. No trainers in the outside section — trainers are found inside the cave. The cave is reached from Route 42 which runs east from Ecruteak City between the two entrances of Mt. Mortar."
